{"tid":2227497,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–自然順產及剖腹取子的其中一道分別","createTime":"2020-10-02T22:33:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T10:00:04.000Z","uid":38861,"like":50,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"9cac21f505c19e1daf331470524552803f97adf2","tid":2227497,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T22:33:33.000Z","msg":"剖腹產子的英文學名為(Caesarean section)，又名C-Section。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A2dnuMm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA2dnuMm.jpg&h=b3880f94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）腸道細菌對於個體的免疫力及消化能力扮演著重要的作用。<br />\n有不少報告指出，順產嬰兒的腸道細菌品種，與母親的相對上接近，而剖腹取子的嬰兒則是非然。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KtwsFS7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKtwsFS7.jpg&h=4113626f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n值得注意的是，順產嬰兒的腸道細菌品種與母親糞便的細菌品種則相當之接近。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）基於這點，芬蘭臨床研究找來了7位剖腹產子的母親(Ref1)，並在其中一次的5ml母乳裡頭混入已確定無致病源的母親糞便(3.5-7mg，產前三星期取得)。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MdAtqjV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMdAtqjV.jpg&h=cb054689&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所有的測試組合中，頭兩個月均由母乳餵哺。他們發現，在剖腹產子且混入已確定無致病源的母親糞便的組別，其中一種腸道細菌品種中，在三星期的時候與自然順產的相當接近;<br />\n<br />\n根據統計，剖腹產子嬰兒的腸道細菌品種，通常在一年過後才會跟自然順產的開始類近。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖4）圖中的各種顏色代表著各腸道細菌品種，可以看見後兩者相對的較為類近。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PA8e5j5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPA8e5j5.jpg&h=abb252b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n腸道細菌品種的不同，對嬰兒日後的健康會有甚麼重要影響，現今的文獻中暫時還沒能取得共識，作者亦會繼續跟進是之研究中的嬰兒日後狀況。<br />\n<br />\n但這研中可是花了非常多的功夫才能篩選中沒有致病源的母親糞便，在沒有適當醫療措施的情況下，作者警告絕對不可獨自試驗，否則只會增加嬰兒患上致命疾病的風險。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmb500bRp0Z5eW4%2BYbKsxGJA%3D&h=8916c786\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmb500bRp0Z5eW4%2BYbKsxGJA%3D&h=cd1286ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.cell.com/cell/fulltext/S0092-8674\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cell.com%2Fcell%2Ffulltext%2FS0092-8674&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmb500bRp0Z5eW4%2BYbKsxGJA%3D&h=749e66c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cell.com/cell/fulltext/S0092-8674</a>(20)31089-8"},{"pid":"a6c62c7eefa15b2bbf6cad67231316c134f92a48","tid":2227497,"uid":371746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T22:34:46.000Z","msg":"頭香<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135e76a7cc27e88f0810240456121f6807adff8b","tid":2227497,"uid":371746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T22:35:49.000Z","msg":"薯仔係未瞓定瞓醒定點，咁早出文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f828d9fc34980596671d9edaaf48db4612d51c21","tid":2227497,"uid":38861,"